title: Ground News - 1 killed in crash between motorcycle, vehicle near Del Valle High School
text:
Summary by Ground News One person died Thursday after a crash involving a motorcycle near Del Valle High School. Crash involved a motorcycle and a vehicle, according to Austin-Travis County EMS. No other people were reported injured. ATCEMS warns drivers to expect delays in the area and use alternate routes if possible. Share menu More

ATCEMS said on social media at 11:23 a.m. medics pronounced one adult dead on the scene of a crash at 5100 Ross Road, which is near the high school.
